= Requirements

- OS: ubuntu, debian or centos


= Overview

This module install and configure fail2ban to ban ssh DoS

== Parameters

- ignoreip : list of ip that fail2ban must not filter


= Usage

  node "mynode" inherits ... {
    class { 'fail2ban': ignoreip => ['208.88.110.46']  }
  }


